data.description: Welcome to this exquisite front courtyard style home located in the highly sought-after Sienna Hills. Complimented by gleaming hardwood floors, stained grade woodwork & an abundance of natural light, the main level boasts formal dining area, great room w/corner stone fireplace, kitchen & nook. Kitchen showcases slab granite counters, sleek stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, tile backsplash, breakfast bar & more. The upstairs owner’s ensuite is a tranquil escape, flooded w/natural light, european-style shower, separate soaker tub, granite counters, decorative mirrors & sophisticated copper sinks. Don’t miss the addt'l 3 generously sized bedrooms, 2 full baths & upstairs flex/living space in this 2,903 SF home. Enjoy private & fully landscaped east facing back yard in cul-de-sac, RV parking, cov'd patios, shed, plus two separate 2-bay garages. Keep active or find solitude as the lifestyle amenities flourish in this sub: community clubhouse, pool, tennis & basketball courts, vineyards & walking paths.
